column5: Headed up to Lac Suel next week. Looking for any fishing reports for the lake that could help get us on them right away. Big thanks in advance for any info.
My father is at Black Bay outpost as I write this, He's back on sat, Ill give his thoughts as soon as I hear from him

I am heading up tomorrow morning and going into Lac Seul Outpost on Wednesday. My friends are there now and report great fishing despite the round of storms that passed through on Saturday and Sunday. Best bite was in the 15 - 20 feet
